code: @Before public void setUp() {     amazonSQSClient = Mockito.mock(AmazonSQSClient.class).     SqsConfiguration config = new SqsConfiguration().     config.setQueueUrl(QUEUE_URL).     config.setAmazonSQSClient(amazonSQSClient).     endpoint = new SqsEndpoint("aws-sqs://test-queue", new SqsComponent(new DefaultCamelContext()), config). }
